    <section class="main-news section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section__title appear appear--bottom">What’s new</h2>
            <div class="section__grid section__grid--3 appear-group">
                                    <a class="card" href="https://visicomdata.com/news/visicom-at-futurecom-2025-discover-the-power-of-geospatial-intelligence">
                        <div class="card__img-wrapper">
                            <img class="lazy card__img" data-src="https://visicomdata.com/raw/news/2025/202-oicture-FTC-prev.jpg" alt="Home">
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="card__title">Visicom At Futurecom 2025: Discover The Power Of Geospatial Intelligence</h3>
                        <p class="card__date">21 Sep 2025</p>
                        <p class="card__text">Futurecom 2025, taking place in São Paulo from September 30 to October 2, is a leading event in connectivity and innovation for Latin America. It will gather over 300 exhibiting brands and more than 30,000 industry professionals, showcasing the latest trends in digital transformation, IoT, AI, and cybersecurity.</p>
                    </a>
                                    <a class="card" href="https://visicomdata.com/news/visicom-at-intergeo-2025">
                        <div class="card__img-wrapper">
                            <img class="lazy card__img" data-src="https://visicomdata.com/raw/news/2025/201-Intergeo2025-prev.jpg" alt="Home">
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="card__title">Visicom at InterGEO 2025, Hall 12.1, Stand 1G060</h3>
                        <p class="card__date">03 Sep 2025</p>
                        <p class="card__text">We are excited to announce our participation in INTERGEO 2025. With over 30 years of experience, VISICOM is a global provider of high-precision DIGITAL MAPPING PRODUCTS. Our solutions serve a wide range of industries, including Telecom, Smart cities, Solar energy, Infrastructure and Urban planning.</p>
                    </a>
                                    <a class="card" href="https://visicomdata.com/news/building-smart-and-green-cities-with-geospatial-data">
                        <div class="card__img-wrapper">
